{"tid":19581,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有無巴打執過自己朋友二灘?","createTime":"2016-12-03T01:10:46.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-03T03:29:21.000Z","uid":17343,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9c217e2b2c34406c623d53faef31706e5dcbd731","tid":19581,"uid":17343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T01:10:46.000Z","msg":"我有個毒撚朋友<br />\n之前成日比我條女撚來撚去<br />\n係咁Whatsapp又成<br />\n我一早看在眼內啦<br />\n果陣已經定計<br />\n玩多幾個月就飛<br />\n<br />\n呢條女都係雞來架啦<br />\n成日扮純情 一早知你係死港女貪錢啦<br />\n條毒撚屋企叫做唔憂<br />\n<br />\n好啦我幾個月錢<br />\n玩完條女<br />\n條毒撚就即刻比隻雞昆左落搭<br />\n宜家幫條女埋單<br />\n<br />\n真係陰功啦<br />\n死港女比人玩撚完<br />\n就搵條毒撚埋單<br />\n<br />\n呀徐生，你之前望住我撚尻你宜家條女<br />\n到底係咩感覺<br />\n二灘好食嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a65fd858981f877671ba97cc014a78bf48a1f4c","tid":19581,"uid":9668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T01:12:42.000Z","msg":"二灘都冇得執個d點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f91c08716c31764a3c22e5728684adc14c281f10","tid":19581,"uid":17343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T01:14:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>二灘都冇得執個d點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n叫雞"},{"pid":"4d5807cf6c5a8a035a1a46c99928c7920b77fdd9","tid":19581,"uid":23902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T01:16:52.000Z","msg":"散咗上黎屌人地條仔有咩意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n上fb講啦"},{"pid":"d1af8765e9dfbdfa0d9a26e1b010127855123344","tid":19581,"uid":5770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T01:17:03.000Z","msg":"有呀 上次個fd 同條女分左手 跟住佢好傷心call 我出黎飲野 果晚大家飲到醉醉地跟住直接去左開房<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  有人想知再講"},{"pid":"dccc60947a6de93a6b550da2222d8ce44cd797f6","tid":19581,"uid":17343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score"